{"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Property","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B41ThemeQuantityInputComponentTokensProviderC12sizeMaxWidthSdvp","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sizeMaxWidth"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"SizeSemanticToken","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic04SizeB5Tokena"}],"title":"sizeMaxWidth","extendedModule":"OUDSThemesOrange","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"symbolKind":"property"},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeQuantityInputComponentTokensProvider"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeQuantityInputComponentTokensProvider\/sizeMaxWidth","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"text":"Has for value token DimensionRawTokens._3000","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemequantityinputcomponenttokensprovider\/sizemaxwidth"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"@objc","kind":"attribute"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sizeMaxWidth"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic04SizeB5Tokena","text":"SizeSemanticToken","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}]}]}],"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeQuantityInputComponentTokensProvider":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeQuantityInputComponentTokensProvider","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of quantity input","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSQuantityInput"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"code":"AllQuantityInputComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeQuantityInputComponentTokensProvider","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It implements also the protocol ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"QuantityInputComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"tag inputs","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Quantity inputs","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemequantityinputcomponenttokensprovider","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","title":"OrangeThemeQuantityInputComponentTokensProvider","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeQuantityInputComponentTokensProvider"}],"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeQuantityInputComponentTokensProvider"}]},"ic_theme_orange.png":{"alt":null,"type":"image","identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ic_theme_orange.png"}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeQuantityInputComponentTokensProvider/sizeMaxWidth":{"abstract":[{"text":"Has for value token DimensionRawTokens._3000","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sizeMaxWidth"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic04SizeB5Tokena","text":"SizeSemanticToken","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemequantityinputcomponenttokensprovider\/sizemaxwidth","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeQuantityInputComponentTokensProvider\/sizeMaxWidth","title":"sizeMaxWidth"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","title":"Theme Orange